{"tid":733752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有片］網傳東莞一間廠辭退打暑期工的學生 學生工資維權遭警察鎮壓毆打","createTime":"2018-07-08T04:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T12:59:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a50b4423f95539e58b94500f6d63174dcdd5f1","tid":733752,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:58:16.000Z","msg":"據說是廣東電白的學生暑期到東莞一家工廠打工解聘後，學生們針對工資問題進行和平維權，遭到大批東莞公安野蠻毆打。面對手無寸鐵和平請願沒有半點過激行為的學生，我厲害過居然棍棒相加，殘酷鎮壓，這毒手大清都沒下過。（下）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/dyrcqybq/status/1015582848349192192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fdyrcqybq%2Fstatus%2F1015582848349192192&d=4I0nUGy1hPUuHKx6tC%2BvADQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a15aeccf\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/dyrcqybq/status/1015582848349192192</a>"},{"pid":"a0107bd3889c93d35c9cfafc01d3942c9168b5ca","tid":733752,"uid":31237,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"肯定大清都沒有過？"},{"pid":"6f7a959bdfc665f78b9eba91f6b6801d7fdd8bcf","tid":733752,"uid":32114,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"a0107bd3889c93d35c9cfafc01d3942c9168b5ca","tid":733752,"uid":31237,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"肯定大清都沒有過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"揚州十日，嘉定三屠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班蝗蟲肯定睇得啲19清宮愛情劇多，以為清朝人日日都係談情說愛爭女扑野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4893613a23131b9e430cedc6d9402b3359b56ad2","tid":733752,"uid":53062,"like":7,"dislike":20,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"暑期工憑咩出糧   俾機會你學野仲嘈嘈閉"},{"pid":"a499574468ff33ba8c658ef284fc91fe5bd38d2b","tid":733752,"uid":13378,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4893613a23131b9e430cedc6d9402b3359b56ad2","tid":733752,"uid":53062,"like":7,"dislike":20,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"re